==================
Django Magic Embed
==================

Easy template tags and tools to embed video and get thumbnails form them.


-------------------
Instalation and use
-------------------
1. python setup.py install
2. add magicembed to INSTALLED_APPS
3. In the template 
...
{% load magicembed %}
...

{{ video|magicembed:"640x480" }}
...
To get a thumbnail url

{{ video|magicthumbnail }}

